                    <h1 class="mb-5">Book A <span class="text-primary text-uppercase">Travel Journey</span></h1>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <div style="display:flex; margin: 50px 0;">
                        <div style="flex: 1;border-radius: 10px 0 0 10px;overflow: hidden;">
                            <img src="/images/HBanner.jpg" alt="anhChuyenDi" style="width: 100%;height: 100%;object-fit: cover;object-position: center;">
                        </div>
                        <div style="flex: 2; padding: 15px 30px; background-color: #f9f9f9;">
                            <h3 style="color: #2d4271;font-size: 22px;font-weight: 700;line-height: 28px;text-align: left;">Thái Lan: Bangkok - Pattaya (Khám phá Bảo tàng Sáp Louis Tussaud Pattaya, chùa Wat Arun, Tặng Buffet tại BaiYoke Sky) | Lễ Té nước</h3>
                            <div style="text-align: left; padding-top:15px;">
                                <p class="tour-info">Mã Tour <b>NNSGN1303-080-160424VU-V-F</b></p>
                                <p class="tour-info">Khởi hành <b>16/04/2024</b></p>
                                <p class="tour-info">Thời gian <b>5 ngày</b></p>
                                <p class="tour-info">Nơi khởi hành <b>TP. Hồ Chí Minh</b></p>
